{"tid":322641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"32C曹思詩「解扣」供樓","createTime":"2017-07-15T04:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T10:19:31.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a91a01e04effef8155358de72f49cd6c7fcf5e","tid":322641,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170714/photo/bkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170715075418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170714%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170715075418&h=c0a63122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不得了！<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的無綫藝人曹思詩（CC）今年推出以香港十大沙灘為主題的個人寫真，喜愛水上運動的CC捱曬捱熱在多個沙灘取景，狂換比堅尼大騷32C上圍加上蜜桃臀，展示陽光性感。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>玩過裸泳</strong><br />\n<br />\n最激一輯，擁有32C身材的CC在沙灘解帶裸背擠出側胸，效果噴血，穿慣比堅尼的CC表示拍攝期間有幾位男泳客眼望望，但已黐了乳貼，加上信任攝影師，故不覺得太尷尬。問到曾否裸曬？CC直言曾在外國裸半身曬太陽，更試過在香港裸泳，回想都覺得刺激：「我個人比較即興，大無畏，試過有晚半夜同幾個女仔朋友去沙灘飲嘢，周圍完全冇人，突然大家提議裸泳，就即刻除衫衝落水，啲水好冰，感覺好正好爽，下次有機會都想試多次，我都覺得自己幾癲。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Keep住搵銀</strong><br />\n<br />\nCC多年前只得17歲時曾推出寫真，其後加入TVB，但暫時仍未正式上位，她直言希望透過出寫真得到更多拍攝機會，目標做個好演員。問到多年來有否經濟壓力，CC自覺幸運：「以前做Model時收入仲多過依家，都儲咗啲錢，依家經濟壓力係要供樓。（自己畀首期？）係父母幫手畀嘅，但要自己供呀！雖然唔算係捱得好慘，但都要Keep住密密做架！要好努力接Job同返大陸登台。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170714/photo/bkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170715075418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170714%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170715075418&h=98b8980a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解扣32C！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170714/photo/bkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170715075418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170714%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170715075418&h=199dfd2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身材火辣辣。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170714/photo/bkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170715075418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170714%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170715075418&h=2885ca5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSexy呢！<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170714/bkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170714%2Fbkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001.html&d=OlRwPETM0fXoJ3tLhRfY1f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f40c4e49\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170714/bkn-20170714233012311-0714_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"379be64a70f794f88c3f420a58a076570ea7a65d","tid":322641,"uid":5253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:17:56.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"72f3f78b5a4cb0ed45a4737ced7141ba9ac835b1","tid":322641,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:18:37.000Z","msg":"唔靚"},{"pid":"fa29a571c693a560ccbb75d2a2aeaafac3f0c830","tid":322641,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"邊位呀"},{"pid":"3d28bf71a181301e598f64c18b07c0b3ada786ba","tid":322641,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"4a873b12a61fc158eeb63d8828ba50441a1f12f4","tid":322641,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3027a3e2b9717ff34f674a25d28d6801a2e9e964","tid":322641,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4687f99ac4b8363bfc81